Elspeth McKendrick, 16, was left shattered in 2012 when doctors diagnosed her with Asperger's syndrome .
She had been an artistic and creative student at Tottington High School .
Her parents said she was 'happy to be odd and eccentric' but was 'very much in denial' about her condition .
